Uses of Package
org.openwms.common.comm.api

  • Packages that use org.openwms.common.comm.api 
    Package Description
    org.openwms.common.comm.api
    Contains telegram implementations specific to the OSIP specification.
    org.openwms.common.comm.err
    Contains classes responsible for dealing with error messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.err.tcp
    Contains classes responsible for dealing with tcp/ip error telegrams.
    org.openwms.common.comm.request
    Contains types according to the RequestMessage handling.
    org.openwms.common.comm.request.tcp
    This package contains types for RequestMessage handling specific to tcp/ip.
    org.openwms.common.comm.router
    Contains implementation following the Router pattern, used to route incoming messages to the right MessageChannel.
    org.openwms.common.comm.tcp
    Contains classes specific to the tcp/ip handling.
    org.openwms.common.comm.transformer.tcp
    Contains transformer implementations responsible to transform incoming messages to domain specific messages.
    org.openwms.common.comm.util
    Utility package referenced by types from the tcp/ip layer.
